Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.ui.actions

This package defines top-level UI related action classes.

Interface Summary
ActionConstants Define a list of constants that are used by menu and some of action definition.

Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.ui.actions Description

This package defines top-level UI related action classes. These classes will be used to support actions on the menu and/or tool bars of MainFrame.
